title: [Lilokia's Armory]
[Lilokia's General Store]
description: An intricate knot-worked wall-hanging hangs on one of the blue watered silk walls, and a modwir beam ceiling rises overhead.  A large potted fern sits in one corner of a sanded pine floor.  There is a carved oak table on one side of the shop and an elegantly carved oak armoire on the other.
